{"tid":299772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我可以講某類既tb係好黑人憎...","createTime":"2017-06-27T10:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T04:54:57.000Z","uid":43697,"like":147,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d88c1054179bf1a4d7ee2004234ce52d91bc0cdf","tid":299772,"uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"你話性別歧視乜都好 我問心依類人係好黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n案件重演:<br />\n<br />\n同屋企人係餐廳到食飯 隔離檯既斜對角 檯與檯之間都有啲距離 咁屋企人背住佢地自然睇唔到佢地做緊乜 <br />\n<br />\n咁好啦 我同屋企人邊講邊食 有講有笑 咁我自己習慣就食下又間唔中周圍望 咁我就望到個邊檯個肥tb一直怒啤住我個方向 咁我唔理繼續食 而佢地張檯有肥tb仲有三條女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n示意圖:<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/27/183611_4d3d1cf614d04ae8065dd32c4c0474a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F27%2F183611_4d3d1cf614d04ae8065dd32c4c0474a5.jpg&h=b3acb786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後隔左一陣 我再抬頭望 我又望到佢一直望住我個邊 我心諗你做乜鳩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好啦 我就同我老母講 後面張檯有個tb係咁望過黎 老母望左眼 跟住叫我咪撚理佢 <br />\n<br />\n到食完埋單時候 我同老豆同埋佢啲朋友一齊行門口先 咁岩tb張檯堆人就係我地前面埋單 我老母埋完單行出黎<br />\n<br />\n無端端佢地條女望撚住我老母 我就聽到佢同個tb口upup講話我老母撞到佢 係到指手劃腳 我就問我老母有無撞到人 老母就答無 有一定會同人講sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同老豆仲有佢啲朋友即刻起曬鋼 埋去佢屌佢老母 條tb比我地疾到聲都唔撚敢出 <br />\n<br />\n黎個總結 以後見到依類人大聲啲就得 但要夠人多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e486d17e3e20542a9f55213256fb33eb60e0216","tid":299772,"uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:54:28.000Z","msg":"講事實出黎都要負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92caaf9d89573fe08c973a10a5e09562c87c4d8","tid":299772,"uid":81698,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T10:58:02.000Z","msg":"Tb正垃圾<br />\n肥tb係垃圾中既垃圾"},{"pid":"9e3cbb6b3dfc0da629db9563e80bfc59b3c29362","tid":299772,"uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T11:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Tb正垃圾<br />\n肥tb係垃圾中既垃圾</blockquote><br />\n都唔知佢啤乜鳩 我地講野正常聲浪內容恰當 無影響到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cece4b52a3196ffee8f257035cd83a30ebbbfb8","tid":299772,"uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T13:19:41.000Z","msg":"推爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82195187cb4db1fd718e80b0bb9cf086af3f7ee","tid":299772,"uid":92704,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T13:22:03.000Z","msg":"某類？<br />\n全部都好撚黑人憎啦"},{"pid":"6b5950c39e68a4054693d7c85b2e509007349c6a","tid":299772,"uid":43697,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T13:23:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>某類？<br />\n全部都好撚黑人憎啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先唔好分肥瘦先啦 有啲tb係幾講得笑 因為我身邊都有個例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd5a50b3d5ffa8a609419500bac376f316301fc","tid":299772,"uid":43697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T08:13:30.000Z","msg":"推 講下大家對tb睇法 歡迎絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6322e06b8d32fcc742f8252f22fe4ed71b7fde","tid":299772,"uid":65931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"我覺得某D TB好鍾意搞事搞非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03be4afc9f22e2c14a78ae1bae95892fc3c7da9a","tid":299772,"uid":43697,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得某D TB好鍾意搞事搞非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尤其是啲肥肥地又高既tb 佢地真係以為自己係男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8aeb385417a97cd60df4d22571d3